    <div class="content-box">
        <p>
            Start managing your garden with Evera! Track your plants, monitor their watering schedules,
            and explore care guides tailored for you.
        </p>
        <p>Use the Sidebar to explore features like:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Adding your plants blah blah....</li>
            <li>Plant schedules blah blah ...... </li>
            <li>Care Tips blah blah .....</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="action-buttons">
        <a class="btn" href="Account/Login">Login</a>
        <a class="btn" href="Account/Register">Register</a>
    </div>
</div>

